messages.content: ComfyUI-PixelOE is a barebones ComfyUI wrapper for the PixelOE library.
Where can I find the source code for the PixelOE library?
The source code for the PixelOE library can be found at https://github.com/KohakuBlueleaf/PixelOE.
Is there any support promised for ComfyUI-PixelOE?
No, the creator cannot promise any support for ComfyUI-PixelOE. They encourage someone else to make a proper node if they feel compelled.
What is the primary purpose of ComfyUI-PixelOE?
ComfyUI-PixelOE is designed to integrate the PixelOE library into the ComfyUI interface for easier and more streamlined use.
Can I expect adequate support for ComfyUI-PixelOE if I encounter issues?
The creator of ComfyUI-PixelOE does not promise any support, so it's likely that you may have to rely on community help or self-troubleshooting.
